    2016-03-20 20:17:34.126 Demo[4084:422492] 这里是同步执行的串行队列02。===> {number = 1, name = main}
    2016-03-20 20:17:34.746 Demo[4084:422514] 串行02 ===> 0 ===> {number = 2, name = (null)}
    2016-03-20 20:17:34.746 Demo[4084:422514] 串行02 ===> 1 ===> {number = 2, name = (null)}
